# webdeck

Web search signals. Runs configured queries and routes findings to crunchdeck.

## Usage
- Configure queries: edit `QUERIES.md`, or `flowdeck blueprint use webdeck-add-query`
- Run all queries: play `queries/TODO.md`
- Findings land under `queries/<slug>/findings/` — activate `send-to-crunchdeck`, `create-card`, or `discard` on each

## Structure
- `QUERIES.md` — the query list (edit to add/remove queries)
- `queries/<slug>/QUERY.md` + `TODO.md` — one per query, with a run log
- `ACTIONS.md` — reference for finding-card actions
